    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/991bd971358515101c679c517b1922d5.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span><br>发现一个程序生成的末日后世界。每个新游戏都提供不同的起点和体验，让您在废弃的地点和道路上收集资源并生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/9bab6a31cdcffa3331c65493a92beb41.poster.avif?t=1762533563\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/9bab6a31cdcffa3331c65493a92beb41.webm?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/9bab6a31cdcffa3331c65493a92beb41.mp4?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/cc13626c88da59a22756b0e0c3e057df.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span><br>从一辆破旧的房车开始您的旅程，修理并升级每个部分。从炉灶和冰箱到厕所和座椅区域，个性化一切，打造您自己的生活空间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/05e731d3b9af6fd06ff762f7fb0b7eb9.poster.avif?t=1762533563\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/05e731d3b9af6fd06ff762f7fb0b7eb9.webm?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/05e731d3b9af6fd06ff762f7fb0b7eb9.mp4?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/9478d114968f7f2d39ffc66d213ab358.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span><br>通过烹饪、钓鱼、修理和制作咖啡等活动存活下来。使用房车的厨房来烹饪您找到的食物，制作更有效的餐食。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/f96c954b894519e3c86651f684fe2f69.poster.avif?t=1762533563\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/f96c954b894519e3c86651f684fe2f69.webm?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/f96c954b894519e3c86651f684fe2f69.mp4?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/7f939043b592c52b47b2da85a416e264.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span><br>发现 Nomad Drive，每个部分都是完全可互动的。从家具到电器，触摸、定制并探索一切，使房车真正成为您的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/dd362be763e4168c07473ee69e7a0096.poster.avif?t=1762533563\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/dd362be763e4168c07473ee69e7a0096.webm?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/dd362be763e4168c07473ee69e7a0096.mp4?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/69ee23517c88dda4b88c49ce651a9938.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span><br>使用太阳能板或燃料驱动的发电机管理能源。利用各种能源来源满足您的房车需求，延长您的生存时间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/eb243b4bb7c8c4df690b21b792a0b7c0.poster.avif?t=1762533563\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/eb243b4bb7c8c4df690b21b792a0b7c0.webm?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/eb243b4bb7c8c4df690b21b792a0b7c0.mp4?t=1762533563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223980/extras/47c6959e8599b07e928418b767a8cac3.webp?t=1762533563\" width=400 height=40 /></span>",
